						               													<description>This game for 2-4 players. Each is equipped with a counter, 2 money bags and a stock of tokens. Players throw the die and move the number of spaces indicated. There are fines and rewards on the different spaces in the game.  Landing on spaces 4, 20 or 29 causes the player to lose a turn. If you land on space 30 (Poor Lady) you must promise to buy her gloves. You move to space #30 and pay a token into the pool.In addition you can, on your turn, place the money bags on any of the servant spaces. When opponents land on those spaces they must add a token to the pool in the center of the board. If you reach space number 32 first you colect all of the tokens in the pool and win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
